snippet.title: OGB
snippet.description: We built a Global Model Earthship in Taos, NM and filmed every step of the process.  Now we're building a self-designed homestead in New York, which evolves upon what I learned in Taos.  Architectural Design, Construction, Permaculture, Forestry, etc.  Hopefully these videos can be of use to others.
